keung.cheng.7/videos/10156566128413014/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkwokkeung.cheng.7%2Fvideos%2F10156566128413014%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=1af98470\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kwokkeung.cheng.7/videos/10156566128413014/</a><br />\n<br />\n執行職務係唔駛出示委任證 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c50edd0639fbc414d71f006e3f5a50804e6ef4","tid":1293803,"uid":214688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:08:47.000Z","msg":"PC仔冇家教<br />\n指揮官冇撚用"},{"pid":"2c2c88d5d5a0707261b9cda48fc803f6eeff9547","tid":1293803,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:14:05.000Z","msg":"執行職務唔駛出示委任證<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kwokkeung.cheng.7/videos/10156566128413014/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkwokkeung.cheng.7%2Fvideos%2F10156566128413014%2F&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=1af98470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kwokkeung.cheng.7/videos/10156566128413014/</a>"},{"pid":"5f773901ffc0622dc2d5e958773d8482dd63f360","tid":1293803,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"【記協請入】旺角記者被警察危險對待實錄<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1293767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1293767</a><br />\n<br />\n文字<br />\n〔12:00〕西洋菜街登打士街交界被驅趕到彌敦道<br />\n從直播中 見到警察追住記者<br />\n當記者問到 係咪去到彌敦道就完 警員又唔回應<br />\n令到記者好似變成示威者咁要設防線<br />\n<br />\n〔12:11〕 在場大部份都係記者及議員譚文豪<br />\n警察將記者定義為譚文豪支持者<br />\n試圖用依個方法去驅散記者 但現場記者大部份都著緊反光衣<br />\n此舉對記者人身安全受到威脅<br />\n（根據現場記者所指 在場只有兩至三名口罩示威者 剩餘九成都係記者）<br />\n<br />\n〔12:16〕 在場記者所見已經冇哂示威者 只有過百名記者在場<br />\n但警察繼續喧嘩 要求記者及議員離開<br />\n基本上 警察已經拎返大部份馬路 逼左記者去家樂坊附近<br />\n但記者不是示威者 警察係冇權力咁樣做！<br />\n<br />\n〔12:20〕 警察再次向記者表示要離開立刻離開<br />\n因為警方要清場以及設下防線<br />\n所以多次要求議員及記者離開<br />\n並指出會以清場方式對待在場人士（約百名記者）<br />\n<br />\n〔12:23〕 警察突然發爛 向記者朋友呼喝<br />\n警察為進行佢地既政治目的 將記者推向議員附近<br />\n完全漠視記者安全 係好逼既情況下記者係十分危險<br />\n記者係有可能會出現人踩人情況<br />\n<br />\n〔12:26〕 警方又發爛 不停以長盾向記者！<br />\n因警方在剛才與兩名議員（譚及區）討論 警方拗唔贏發爛<br />\n不停推進在場記者 <br />\n在場只有記者及議員 係唔明白點解記者要被警察如此對待<br />\n<br />\n〔12:35〕 警察叫記者唔好再行一步 否則警察都會再推進<br />\n有人問點解岩岩先打在場記者 以及用盾夾記者<br />\n無一警察作出回應！"},{"pid":"cec8b876bea06b35386bf63f9c73a7973f40c4eb","tid":1293803,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"黑警不放示威者離開<br />\n(已backup)黑警打人 撩人隻秋#24<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfyFRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfyFRS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5rfzFZSWEPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5rfzFZSWEPs&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=3988bde6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5rfzFZSWEPs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2509009319130549\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2509009319130549&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=970b2ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2509009319130549</a>"},{"pid":"3728ebd7630645fb0aa7b5dc5f8d004cd4c82ad4","tid":1293803,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:16:13.000Z","msg":"集中哂佢<br />\n一份監警會<br />\n一份登報"},{"pid":"4fef407e62da615aa50bfc49628169b050d8e981","tid":1293803,"uid":189430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f773901ffc0622dc2d5e958773d8482dd63f360","tid":1293803,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"【記協請入】旺角記者被警察危險對待實錄<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1293767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1293767</a><br />\n<br />\n文字<br />\n〔12:00〕西洋菜街登打士街交界被驅趕到彌敦道<br />\n從直播中 見到警察追住記者<br />\n當記者問到 係咪去到彌敦道就完 警員又唔回應<br />\n令到記